item.description: http://www.facebook.c... Come on down to the Ron Paul HQ in Concord for a night of good old fashion fun. Sen. Jim Forsythe is an avid board game collector and will have many on hand as we spend the night playing games and making phone calls for Dr. Paul. Looking to have some fun with Ron Paul supporters? Think Jim needs to be taken down a step in a game of Stratego? Most importantly, do want to help Dr. Paul win the NH GOP Primary? Then swing on in and lets make this happen *note - Jim might not bring Stratego*
item.name: Game Night and Phone Bank
